<text>==Events==
*End of the Western Zhou dynasty in China as Western barbarian tribes sack the capital Hao. The King You of Zhou is killed. Crown Prince Ji Yijiu escapes to the East where he reigns as King Ping of Zhou.

==Births==

* Romulus and Remus

==Deaths==
*King You of Zhou, King of the Zhou Dynasty of China.

